<p>We hand-deliver microgreens to nine neighborhoods across the Orlando metro. One route per day, harvested the morning of delivery, no middleman.</p>

<h2>Friday morning route — Seminole County</h2>

<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;width:min(80ch,92%);margin:24px auto">
{% for city in cities %}{% if city.route == "Friday morning route" %}
  <a href="/delivery/{{ city.slug }}/" style="display:block;padding:18px;background:var(--cream-shadow);border:2px solid var(--ink);text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink);font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace">
    <strong style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.2rem;display:block;margin-bottom:6px">{{ city.name }}</strong>
    <span style="font-size:0.9rem">Friday morning</span>
  </a>
{% endif %}{% endfor %}
</div>

